{"lastModified":1775133251575,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nA Harmonious Blend of Elegance and Innovation\n\nThe Champ Atlantis is a stunning fusion of performance, style, and comfort, designed for cruising, entertaining, and exploring. Its transformable bow, rotating cockpit, and drop-down sides set it apart, offering flexibility and ease for any occasion.\n\nInside, the spacious saloon with panoramic windows creates a light-filled, inviting atmosphere, while the expansive flybridge offers sunbathing and shaded dining areas with beautiful views.\n\n Accommodating up to 6 guests in three luxurious cabins, including a master cabin and a VIP cabin, the Champ Atlantis is designed for ultimate comfort. It features a teak-decked cockpit, swim platform, and an array of water toys including a stand-up paddleboard and snorkeling gear.\n\nWith high-speed Wi-Fi, TVs in the saloon and cabins, and a fully equipped galley, this yacht ensures a seamless, connected experience. The Champ Atlantis delivers the perfect balance of elegance, innovation, and adventure on the water.\n\n\"Champ Atlantis“ is a sleek, luxury vessel combining elegance and cutting-edge technology for unforgettable marine adventures. Perfect for cruising, entertainment, and exploration.\" The transformable bow, rotating cockpit area and the drop down sides were the highlights noticed by customers and industry professionals alike.\n\nThe Meaning Behind \"Champ Atlantis\"\n\nThe name \"Champ Atlantis\" embodies a sense of luxury, power, and mystery.\nChamp suggests excellence, victory, and strength, representing a yacht that stands out as a champion on the seas, offering unparalleled performance and refined elegance.\nAtlantis evokes the legendary lost city, symbolizing adventure, exploration, and timeless allure. It conjures visions of a mythical paradise beneath the waves, inviting those aboard to discover hidden treasures and new horizons.\n\nTogether, \"Champ Atlantis\" captures the essence of a prestigious vessel, where high performance meets the allure of the unknown.","blueprint":{"name":"CHAMP ATLANTIS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fce55e0-fdc5-11ef-af31-392d3091b277/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fd9a080-fdc5-11ef-9223-0552c5d1c0f5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fd9eea0-fdc5-11ef-8a9b-39534c31f189/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fc1f9d0-fdc5-11ef-a587-8b4e702e6bef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fbf13a0-fdc5-11ef-a587-8b4e702e6bef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fc1abb0-fdc5-11ef-a587-8b4e702e6bef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fcd1d60-fdc5-11ef-8a9a-39534c31f189/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fcd6b80-fdc5-11ef-af31-392d3091b277/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fd7f2d0-fdc5-11ef-af31-392d3091b277/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fcd1d60-fdc5-11ef-af31-392d3091b277/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fcea400-fdc5-11ef-8a9b-39534c31f189/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fbf61c0-fdc5-11ef-a587-8b4e702e6bef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562::assets::0fc29610-fdc5-11ef-a587-8b4e702e6bef/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bef0a3a0-f332-11ee-bfc6-0326d82db562